want as a form of government do we want a continuation of the 
direction you have taken us in state control big state spending 
more mandates or do we want a government founded on people 
this is bernhardts first bid for statewide office a 
businessman from londonderry he has served in the vermont house 
for eight years most recently as the republican leader 
kunin says she is proud of what her administration has 
accomplished and believes she will do well if she can get the 
word out on what we have done especially in the area of the 
environment and education 
i am glad i am a strong environmentalist that i have put my 
neck out on these laws and i am going to fight to put them there 
and not backtrack she said 
chief among the environmental successes cited by the governor is 
a highly controversial law adopted this year designed to ease 
development pressures in this state of 548000 people 
passage of the law stemmed from growing fears among many that 
development primarily vacation homes and resorts was threatening 
to destroy the smalltown simplicity of the nations most rural 
state 
