investigating possible violations by marcos supporters in hawaii 
and california of the neutrality act with regard to the philippines 
supporters of marcos allegedly provided a private boeing 707 
that flew into honolulu last year but departed without marcos after 
federal agents threatened to restrain him if he tried to leave 
us officials are convinced that marcos continues to try to 
destabilize the government of president corazon aquino marcos 
denies such efforts 
